  <steps>
    <step num="0">Heat the pot over medium heat. </step>
    <step num="1">Melt the butter in the pot. </step>
    <step num="2">Cook the garlic until it starts to brown. </step>
    <step num="3">Add the shrimp, salt, and pepper, cooking until shrimp is pink all the way through. </step>
    <step num="4">Add the lemon juice, chili flakes, and parsley. </step>
